Which of the following is a gamification strategy for learning?

According to eLearning Industry, point systems, badges, leaderboards, and challenges are all gamification strategies for learning. However, gamification can be a lot more than just these common tools! Other gamification strategies may include avatars, cooperative play, easter eggs, exploration, negotiating, riddle solving, role playing, and storytelling just to name a few.
